Class BooleanFormulaTransformationVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sosy_lab.java_smt.api.visitors.BooleanFormulaTransformationVisitor

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NNFVisitor

    public abstract class BooleanFormulaTransformationVisitor
extends Object
implements BooleanFormulaVisitor<BooleanFormula>
    Base class for visitors for boolean formulas that recursively transform boolean formulas.
    See Also:
    BooleanFormulaManager.transformRecursively(org.sosy_lab.java_smt.api.BooleanFormula, org.sosy_lab.java_smt.api.visitors.BooleanFormulaTransformationVisitor)
